rules.name: myRule_1
rules.label: When an Audit event is created

recordCreates.name: myRule_1_A1
recordCreates.label: Send introductory email to audited instructor

value.stringValue: • Introduce yourself, the process and conduct a warm handoff to Program Advisor for coaching • Send Travel Information request. Upon completed return, schedule travel and logistics
Send introductory email to audited instructor
• Review coaching call notes in Salesforce from Program Advisor • Send a check-in email to audited instructor [you’ve arrived and will plan to be onsite the next day at ___ a.m.]

• Compile a detailed report of the observed program. For any score in the module that scored a “3” or below, provide a justification for that score in the module notes. • Have the completed report reviewed prior to sending to audited instructor

• Review findings of the audit and debrief report. • If Pass with Observations attach PCI Agreement and provide seals. • If Pass with Corrective Actions, actions must be completed before providing the above.
• Upload signed PCI Agreement; Final Audit Report; Evaluation Form. • Don't forget to send internal message notifying of PCI addition.
